        TOPOF THE NEWS A5 THE STRAITS TIMES MONDAY, AUGUST 24, 2020 | | | OVERWHELMI­NG DEMAND The logistics became so intense that we had to rent more vehicles to do deliveries. We even had to reject some orders because it was hitting 11,000 meals at one point. ’’ MR CLEMENT TIANG, Kim Paradise managing director, on the surge in demand for daily tingkat meals during the circuit breaker. a big part of industry sales. While our tingkat side is doing well, it doesn’t make up for the losses in the buffet sector,” he said.
Similarly, while FattyDaddy­FattyMummy has been serving up more tingkat meals, it has been all quiet on the buffet front.
“There is zero business, even though the seventh month period is usually the best time for catering businesses,” said Ms Lim. Tingkat orders make up about 70 per cent of her business, and the remaining 30 per cent has been bolstered by meal orders for a small foreign workers dormitory.
“When the dorm order ends, that is when the real battle starts because no buffet orders are coming in and who knows when they will resume,” she said. tammei@sph.com.sg Brought to you by the Singapore Tourism Board With strict checks, clean-ups and a green smiley... SingapoRed­iscovers safely More than a cheery logo, the SG Clean quality mark is a bill of health for tourism- and lifestyle-related businesses while offering visitors peace of mind QA & What is the SG Clean programme about? Explore our backyard What does the SG Clean certificat­ion mean for me? Planning to revisit old hangouts or uncover new experience­s in Singapore? There are plenty of deals to enjoy and activities to do to support local businesses and tourism. How do I know if an establishm­ent or a business is SG Clean-certified? Scan this QR code for promotions and discounts on the official SingapoRed­iscover website How are establishm­ents certified SG Clean? GR APHIC: SINGAP ORE TOURISM BOARD you ask, we answer PRINTED AND DISTRIBUTE­D BY PRESSREADE­R PressReade­r.com +1 604 278 4604 ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY . ORIGINAL COPY COPYRIGHT AND PROTECTED BY APPLICABLE LAW
